1
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:11,220
♪Dark clouds shroud the long trail
where the sun descends♪

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,980
♪Must we only meet by chance
and never again?♪

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,900
♪To be parted forever in an instant♪

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:19,660
♪The sighs of passing years♪

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,700
♪When your smile is embedded
in the starry night♪

6
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:25,740
♪We are puppets of twisted fates♪

7
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,620
♪Constantly intertwining♪

8
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:31,660
♪Dissolving in the crowd♪

9
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,940
♪Perhaps out of reach and out of sight♪

10
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:37,260
♪Constantly flashing through my dreams♪

11
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:45,100
♪The sudden icy wind blurs my vision♪

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:50,660
♪The rain drew that day to an end♪

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:54,380
♪How I wish your beauty♪

14
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:59,460
♪I want to love you,
love you, love you, love you♪

15
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,860
[My Divine Emissary]

16
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:13,980
[Episode 4]

17
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,390
My clothes are now dirty.

18
00:01:29,650 --> 00:01:30,320
Lu Huan,

19
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:31,840
deduct his pay.

20
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:32,460
Yes.

21
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:34,260
Deduct my pay?

22
00:01:36,490 --> 00:01:38,080
I would rather you didn't catch me.

23
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,260
After returning to the capital,

24
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,560
the first banquet you host
for the other ministers

25
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:50,740
just had to be on the same day

26
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,050
as His Majesty's flower viewing.

27
00:01:52,050 --> 00:01:53,930
What is there to admire about flowers?

28
00:01:54,330 --> 00:01:55,930
Do you think he's doing it on purpose?

29
00:01:56,740 --> 00:01:58,010
Is everything done?

30
00:01:58,110 --> 00:01:58,780
All done.

31
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,220
No one is likely
to go to His Majesty's event.

32
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:02,630
I go to him,

33
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:03,850
yet he avoids me.

34
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,050
Thus, I want him to come to me.

35
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:08,750
By the way,

36
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:11,600
I have something to tell you.

37
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,200
Recently, a young eunuch

38
00:02:13,290 --> 00:02:14,900
has been spotted by His Majesty's side.

39
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,820
His Majesty dotes on him.

40
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:17,820
It is because of that eunuch

41
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:20,170
that a few of us were culled.

42
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,630
I got it.

43
00:02:22,170 --> 00:02:23,510
I'll have Zhui Ying look into it.

44
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:27,740
Wan,

45
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:30,730
I will make Qi Yan pay the price,

46
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,560
so that you can openly
return to my side.

47
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,180
Don't slack off.

48
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,260
Keep working.

49
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:40,400
Did I tell you to put it here?

50
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:42,780
Go.

51
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:48,020
I can't catch a break with any of you.

52
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:01,170
A banquet hosted by His Majesty
is just exhausting.

53
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:04,010
I can't do it.

54
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,530
I can't move another inch.

55
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:08,640
Eunuch Li,

56
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,130
come help us.

57
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,410
Where is he?

58
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,650
Eunuch Li?

59
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:14,540
Is he slacking off again?

60
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,820
Eunuch Li?

61
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,080
Have you see Eunuch Li?

62
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:19,660
Back to work.

63
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:22,180
Where is he?

64
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,900
Don't slow down.

65
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:27,140
Keep working.

66
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:42,930
Minister Wu,

67
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,720
we will keep your gifts with care

68
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:46,170
and hand it to His Majesty
at the banquet.

69
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,840
Thank you, Eunuch.

70
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,960
His Majesty is hosting a banquet
on the same day as Prince Heqin.

71
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:54,150
What should we do?

72
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:55,110
It's fine.

73
00:03:55,970 --> 00:03:57,690
His Majesty will always host a banquet.

74
00:03:57,690 --> 00:03:58,800
He just want gifts.

75
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:00,210
Our gifts have been given.

76
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:01,240
We'll just excuse ourselves tonight.

77
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,800
It is Prince Heqin's first banquet

78
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,110
since returning to the capital.

79
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:05,830
The power to Qi Kingdom's military

80
00:04:05,830 --> 00:04:07,240
is all in Prince Heqin's hands.

81
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:08,600
We can't embarrass him.

82
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,240
That is true.

83
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:11,570
There are so many ministers
that we won't be missed.

84
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,000
Let's go.

85
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,110
Two banquets on the same day?

86
00:04:20,650 --> 00:04:23,190
I also want to attend Prince Heqin's
welcoming banquet,

87
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:26,660
but there's work to do at night.

88
00:04:27,210 --> 00:04:27,770
Whatever.

89
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,070
I'll sleep for a while longer.

90
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,400
Why is no one here?

91
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,170
Have they all excused themselves?

92
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:39,890
Your Majesty,

93
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:43,080
the ministers are not here,

94
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,520
but their gifts are.

95
00:04:48,290 --> 00:04:48,980
Bring them out.

96
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:57,650
Open it.

97
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,070
Wait. This...

98
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,440
Eunuch Li,

99
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,840
why are you here?

100
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:21,490
For slacking off at work,

101
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,490
deduct his wage.

102
00:05:22,490 --> 00:05:22,980
Yes.

103
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,750
Look into this.

104
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,400
Where have our ministers gone?

105
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:26,830
Yes.

106
00:05:27,930 --> 00:05:28,800
Your Majesty,

107
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,900
If I know the answer,

108
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,360
will you count it
as making up for my mistake

109
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,350
and not deduct my wage?

110
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:38,240
Minister Wang,

111
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,180
[Prince Heqin's Residence]

112
00:05:39,180 --> 00:05:40,500
you're here.

113
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:43,900
Is it really okay

114
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:44,740
on His Majesty's side?

115
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,230
The Emperor has arrived.

116
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:54,990
Prince Heqin's banquet tonight

117
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:56,240
is quite lively.

118
00:05:59,490 --> 00:06:01,540
Isn't this Vice Minister Dong?

119
00:06:02,370 --> 00:06:04,680
We recall you excused yourself
due to diarrhea.

120
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,030
You recovered so quickly.

121
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:08,610
Also, Minister Wu.

122
00:06:09,690 --> 00:06:10,710
Didn't you excuse yourself

123
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:12,240
because your mother is sick?

124
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:13,440
Well?

125
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,820
Is it diarrhea as well?

126
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,950
Also, Minister Zhang.

127
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,990
Has your business trip brought you
to Prince Heqin's Residence?

128
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,320
All rise.

129
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,860
Thank you, Your Majesty.

130
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:31,710
Prince Heqin.

131
00:06:32,730 --> 00:06:34,300
I have come to welcome you as well.

132
00:06:35,550 --> 00:06:36,090
What is it?

133
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,500
Don't you welcome me?

134
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:38,890
Of course, I do.

135
00:06:39,450 --> 00:06:41,550
I have been waiting
for Your Majesty this whole time.

136
00:06:41,730 --> 00:06:43,750
Prince Heqin is still the kind one.

137
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,550
I hear Your Majesty's banquet tonight

138
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:55,350
has been canceled

139
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,400
as no one showed up.

140
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:57,950
We would also like to know

141
00:06:58,350 --> 00:06:59,520
why my ministers

142
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,620
all excused themselves

143
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:02,790
or fallen ill

144
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:03,960
yet still appear

145
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,700
at your residence.

146
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,100
Perhaps it is because Your Majesty

147
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,020
have lost the ministers' loyalty

148
00:07:10,590 --> 00:07:12,690
due to lack of seriousness

149
00:07:12,930 --> 00:07:14,020
and being disrespectful to them.

150
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,860
In that case,

151
00:07:17,670 --> 00:07:19,200
does this mean the loyalty I lost

152
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:22,050
all went over to you, Prince Heqin?

153
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:24,180
I would not dare.

154
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,920
Don't be so nervous.

155
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:28,950
The main purpose

156
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,330
of my attendance

157
00:07:30,330 --> 00:07:31,590
is to welcome Prince Heqin.

158
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:32,850
Everyone, back to your seats.

159
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

160
00:07:35,550 --> 00:07:36,250
Prince Heqin,

161
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:37,340
come.

162
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:39,390
It has been three years
since we last met.

163
00:07:39,810 --> 00:07:40,770
We'll give you a toast.

164
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,990
Why are you so lifeless?

165
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,780
Weren't you quite lively just now?

166
00:07:52,140 --> 00:07:54,180
Why don't we have Prince Heqin

167
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,860
act as the host

168
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:57,570
and put on a performance

169
00:07:57,690 --> 00:07:58,260
to liven up the party?

170
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,930
I will do my best.

171
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,100
Great skills!

172
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:18,980
Great skills!

173
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:23,900
Amazing!

174
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:25,900
Great!

175
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:27,060
Prince Heqin is skilled.

176
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:27,880
How amazing!

177
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:55,900
Great!

178
00:08:55,900 --> 00:08:57,060
What great swordsmanship!

179
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:58,420
What great skills!

180
00:08:58,420 --> 00:08:59,020
Great!

181
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:01,230
Are you satisfied, Your Majesty?

182
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:04,000
You really are a great general of mine.

183
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,900
It is your turn now, Your Majesty.

184
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,750
I have been practicing my archery.

185
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:13,500
I have improved.

186
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:16,550
Would you grant me the honor,
Prince Heqin?

187
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:21,980
You have spent years in the battlefield.

188
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:23,270
You shouldn't be afraid
of my archery, right?

189
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:25,570
It's too dangerous.

190
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:26,360
No way.

191
00:09:26,570 --> 00:09:26,990
Your Majesty,

192
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:28,250
Prince Heqin will be hurt.

193
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:28,880
You do it then.

194
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,960
Weren't you saying Prince Heqin
is stronger than me?

195
00:09:33,260 --> 00:09:34,750
Time to show you who is stronger.

196
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:06,740
Great archery!

197
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:07,980
His Majesty is great at archery!

198
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:09,180
How accurate!

199
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:10,300
Extremely accurate!

200
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:28,580
Great!

201
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,740
Great!

202
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,980
Prince Heqin is amazing!

203
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:34,780
Very amazing, Prince Heqin!

204
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:38,190
You really are highly skilled,
Prince Heqin!

205
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,660
For three years,

206
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,860
you've secured the borders

207
00:10:41,010 --> 00:10:41,970
and engaged in battles,

208
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,960
killing thousands.

209
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:45,570
While you have returned to the capital

210
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,220
without permission or summons,

211
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,920
as you have done well in battle,

212
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:53,520
We have a gift for you.

213
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:55,340
Lu Huan.

214
00:10:58,140 --> 00:10:59,880
You are past the age of marriage,

215
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:01,950
yet you don't have a wife.

216
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:05,310
We have decided to give you

217
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:06,510
a Child-Giving Guanyin

218
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:11,040
May you find a good match

219
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,450
and grow a family soon.

220
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:20,460
Thank you, Your Majesty.

221
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:24,290
We will return to admire the flowers.

222
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,780
You guys have fun.

223
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,420
Farewell, Your Majesty.

224
00:11:38,010 --> 00:11:38,790
Start counting.

225
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:47,900
There is quite a lot.

226
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,980
There is more than last month.

227
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,310
It looks like Prince Heqin's ruckus

228
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:54,720
wasn't such a loss.

229
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:57,240
Last month?

230
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,490
Do you host a banquet every month?

231
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:00,990
Not really.

232
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:03,150
Sometimes, it's two times a month.

233
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,020
Sometimes, it's three.

234
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,820
Are you short on money, Your Majesty?

235
00:12:10,110 --> 00:12:11,680
Don't ask about what you shouldn't know.

236
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,400
How nice to be an emperor.

237
00:12:17,850 --> 00:12:18,900
At my hometown,

238
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:20,820
we only receive this many gifts

239
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:23,790
during birthdays, weddings,

240
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:25,170
and celebrations of new births.

241
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:31,170
Lu Huan,

242
00:12:31,650 --> 00:12:32,760
make sure to count all the money.

243
00:12:33,130 --> 00:12:33,900
Yes.

244
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:34,470
Kong An,

245
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:36,210
send the money to Minister Li.

246
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,920
The aqueduct repair must not be delayed.

247
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:38,430
Yes.

248
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:42,010
We will take a walk.

249
00:12:50,490 --> 00:12:52,020
Why must you always speak up?

250
00:12:52,020 --> 00:12:53,720
Did I say something wrong again?

251
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:57,600
Today is His Majesty's birthday.

252
00:12:57,810 --> 00:12:58,290
Huh?

253
00:12:58,890 --> 00:12:59,850
Why not celebrate it then?

254
00:13:00,690 --> 00:13:02,760
His Majesty doesn't like
celebrating his birthday.

255
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:03,570
You...

256
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:36,830
You can't catch me.

257
00:13:36,830 --> 00:13:37,540
Your Majesty.

258
00:13:37,540 --> 00:13:38,940
Slow down, Your Majesty.

259
00:13:38,940 --> 00:13:39,820
You can't catch me.

260
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,260
Slow down, Your Majesty.

261
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:42,620
Yan.

262
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:44,020
It's my birthday today.

263
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,500
Play with me, please?

264
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,420
Yan,

265
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,760
just look at the time.

266
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,600
Why are you still wearing this?

267
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:52,500
Get His Majesty changed.

268
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,570
I don't want to get changed.

269
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,580
I still want to play.

270
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,280
Also, I don't like
celebrating my birthday.

271
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:57,810
Every time,

272
00:13:57,870 --> 00:13:59,460
I will be sitting alone up top.

273
00:13:59,580 --> 00:14:01,140
I can't do this. I can't do that.

274
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:01,860
Your Majesty,

275
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,120
have you forgotten the etiquette

276
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,780
taught by the Imperial Mentor?

277
00:14:06,450 --> 00:14:07,870
You are no longer the crown prince.

278
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:08,940
You are the ruler of a kingdom.

279
00:14:09,420 --> 00:14:11,490
You must act with propriety.

280
00:14:11,610 --> 00:14:12,330
Do you understand?

281
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,720
I listen to you all the time.

282
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:14,460
What is the point

283
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,780
of being an emperor?

284
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,680
How can you say that?

285
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,420
You are the ruler of a kingdom.

286
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,420
How can you be selfish?

287
