537
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:26,480
However, right now,

538
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:27,760
there is discontent among the citizens.

539
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:29,050
Their lives are hard.

540
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:31,050
