574
00:27:50,540 --> 00:27:51,150
Leave.

575
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:54,240
Yes.

576
00:28:03,120 --> 00:28:03,530
Your Majesty,

577
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:04,740
I have completed

578
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:05,970
what I promised you.

579
00:28:13,820 --> 00:28:15,610
We have never seen
such a way canals could be built.

580
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,480
Is this from your hometown as well?

581
00:28:24,210 --> 00:28:25,000
However,

582
00:28:25,460 --> 00:28:27,000
there are no numbers on here.

583
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:28,870
That...

584
00:28:29,360 --> 00:28:31,760
That is because the blueprint
will be very complicated then.

585
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,760
I don't specialize in this.

586
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:35,760
Please ask Scholar Zhen

587
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:38,840
to complete the draft.

588
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,440
Yes.

589
00:28:45,010 --> 00:28:45,590
The blueprint...

590
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:53,110
I'm up so early,

591
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:54,620
yet I don't get an afternoon nap.

592
00:28:54,710 --> 00:28:56,420
It's illogical.

593
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:57,240
If you can't wake up,

594
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:58,850
just tell His Majesty.

595
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:00,450
He is not that kind.

596
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,250
It's him.

597
00:29:07,230 --> 00:29:09,630
Are they looking at me or you?

598
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:10,940
Of course, it's you.

599
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:11,780
Why me?

600
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:12,620
Don't you know?

601
00:29:12,620 --> 00:29:13,140
Know what?

602
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:16,550
There is so much gossip in the palace.

603
00:29:16,850 --> 00:29:19,370
It won't be good for me
to tell you, the star of it all.

604
00:29:20,010 --> 00:29:20,920
Tell me.

605
00:29:26,590 --> 00:29:27,080
In the past,

606
00:29:27,530 --> 00:29:29,400
His Majesty refused to do it
with Consort Wan.

607
00:29:29,890 --> 00:29:30,650
After some time,

608
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:32,180
people are saying

609
00:29:32,230 --> 00:29:33,630
that His Majesty likes men.

610
00:29:35,730 --> 00:29:36,460
And?

611
00:29:36,690 --> 00:29:37,550
Last night,

612
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:39,550
a few eunuchs

613
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:42,950
saw you and His Majesty
in the Imperial Garden...

614
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:44,950
What were you doing?

615
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:49,860
Look.

616
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:50,740
Who is His Majesty with?

617
00:29:50,850 --> 00:29:51,670
It's Eunuch Li.

618
00:29:56,310 --> 00:29:57,250
How can it be?

619
00:29:59,710 --> 00:30:00,720
I'm a girl.

620
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:01,690
I know that.

621
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:02,830
Does His Majesty know?

622
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,000
If he doesn't know,

623
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,760
could it be he really likes men?

624
00:30:10,570 --> 00:30:12,720
Why else would His Majesty's harem
be so empty?

625
00:30:13,270 --> 00:30:15,040
Even on the night he spent
with Consort Wan,

626
00:30:15,330 --> 00:30:16,200
I hear

627
00:30:16,490 --> 00:30:17,950
he used a drug.

628
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:28,500
Look.

629
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,140
[Why Must the Emperor Marry Me?]

630
00:30:33,190 --> 00:30:35,900
Why Must the Emperor Marry Me?

631
00:30:40,990 --> 00:30:42,310
What is this trash you always read?

632
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:43,800
Don't look down on it.

633
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:45,520
This book is very popular.

634
00:30:46,330 --> 00:30:47,320
This book writes

635
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:50,680
that an emperor fell in love
with a eunuch,

636
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:54,590
but the eunuch
is actually a girl in disguise.

637
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:57,560
What then?

638
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:01,760
Then, when the Empress Dowager
found out,

639
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:05,180
she believed it was treason
to lie to the Emperor,

640
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:09,320
so the eunuch was killed.

641
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:14,540
No way.

642
00:31:14,990 --> 00:31:15,990
This palace is too dangerous.

643
00:31:16,320 --> 00:31:17,560
I must find some water to go home.

644
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:19,780
♪You're the legend of the future♪

645
00:31:19,780 --> 00:31:21,570
♪A guest from tomorrow♪

646
00:31:21,630 --> 00:31:23,320
♪The stars we once gazed♪

647
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:25,320
♪Used to flow through your veins♪

648
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:27,320
♪I must have heard it in a dream♪

649
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:28,910
♪You agree in my ear♪

650
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,490
♪Love is the soul of life♪

651
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:42,760
♪When a gust of wind brushes past♪

652
00:31:42,760 --> 00:31:46,320
♪The sand and wind burn with passion♪

653
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:49,400
♪Unafraid to forego a chance
to quench our thirst♪

654
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:53,200
♪Like camels walking with eyes closed♪

655
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:56,320
♪When the rain falls
into a rare silence♪

656
00:31:56,320 --> 00:32:00,040
♪Thinking of hardships
you and I don't know♪

657
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:03,040
♪No need to hum the wind's song♪

658
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:07,120
♪Uncaring of the darkening skies♪

659
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:08,800
♪I understood all that for you♪

660
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,560
♪But you have disappeared♪

661
00:32:10,560 --> 00:32:12,240
♪I am lost in the dark♪

662
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,960
♪How should I stop?♪

663
00:32:13,960 --> 00:32:15,640
♪Loving you feels like another lifetime♪

664
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:19,320
♪But yearning flows into a poem♪

665
00:32:19,320 --> 00:32:22,280
♪For us to meet again♪

666
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:25,640
♪Requires the promise of millenia♪

667
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:27,880
♪Watching the rain hail down♪

668
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:32,960
♪It's like you're still beside me♪

669
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:35,920
♪When I want to cross over♪

670
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:40,000
♪To touch you♪

671
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,440
♪But I can't see your fading face♪

672
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:46,720
♪On the opposite shore♪

673
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:49,720
♪How do I voice this?♪

674
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:53,120
♪This heart beats uneasily♪

675
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:56,040
♪How I long to hold you close♪

676
00:32:56,040 --> 00:33:00,400
♪The loneliness in my hands♪

677
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:03,400
♪Yet you warn me♪

678
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:07,440
♪Any closer and I'll set in stone♪

679
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:09,040
♪The sunset deep in your heart♪

680
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:16,920
♪Of the day you most loved me♪
